PrecisAuthority to transfer certain Crown property to TOP NOTCH FEEDS LTD., more particularly, the ownership of a mobile grain inspection unit consisting of one ATCO trailer (8' x 24') which is to be permanently installed near the elevators of Top Notch in the Town of Port Stanley, Ontario, in exchange for the free use of the facility by the Canadian Grain Commission for a period of ten (10) years.
